        "subtitle": "1. He’ll Actually Use It Every Day",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_63.png",
        "content": "<p>Most gifts get their moment when the wrapping paper comes off… and that’s about it. A gift card gets stuffed in a wallet and forgotten. A novelty gadget gets played with once or twice, then disappears into a toolbox or a desk drawer.<br/><br/>A <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>rugged smartwatch</strong></span> is different. It goes on his wrist in the morning and stays there all day. When he’s at work, he glances at it to see who’s calling without digging his phone out of a dirty pocket. When his hands are full, he can quickly check a message and decide if it’s worth stopping what he’s doing. When the day finally slows down, it’s still on his wrist, tracking how much he’s moved and how hard he’s pushed.<br/><br/>Instead of a gift that shows up once a month, you’re giving him <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>the best work watch</strong></span> that quietly shows up every single day.<br/></p>",
